      "index": 3,
      "text": "I can hear the sound of splintering hardwood. They're coming through the door, and I'm out of time.\n\nI pray that I will see you again. But if I don't—I <i>need you</i> to win this war. Do whatever you have to do, just… finish it. Not for me, but for our people. Goodbye.",
